  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as far as-- as that controlling your action on-- on-- on a person who's an adult, I-- to me, I-- they use that in the courts and everything else, and I-- I just don't see it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's affected my life in-- in-- in-- in-- in ways that I think-- I think that-- that I see life from a different angle, definitely, because of my background and experiences.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- I'm not in the groove of the average person who's-- who's had the-- the normal growing up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, you have childhood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You go to nursery school or grade this and that, with parents, and you grow up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You-- you-- then, you know, like, adolescents, teenager.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never knew what a teenager was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Never heard of the expression till I came to this country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I lived through it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm sure I had emotions that changed and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And nothing-- see, here nothing's-- it wasn't labeled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here, everything's labeled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I sometimes get into, like, discussions with my wife about this, that we don't seem to see the same because, I tell her, I don't see the same because I'm not in that groove.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't accept everything on face value, like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't help in this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the way, I'm sure it-- because, like, my past and experiences and the way I grew up has affected me in-- in the-- in a way that-- that's the way I am.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, it's like-- like they say, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] never to let it happen again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only way to never let it happen again is to understand that this could happen again.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
